OL,3,CWoman hit by car in retail park had
OL,4,Cbeen 'dedicated' teacher
OL,6,FThe family of a former teacher from
OL,7,FTeesside have paid tribute to her
OL,8,Fafter she was hit by a car and died
OL,9,Fjust days before Christmas.
OL,11,FRita Grimshaw, 81, was taken to
OL,12,Fhospital for treatment following the
OL,13,Fincident at Silverlink Retail Park, in
OL,14,FNorth Shields, shortly after 5pm on 22
OL,15,FDecember.
OL,17,FEmergency services were called after a
OL,18,Freport that a woman had been struck as
OL,19,Fshe crossed the road outside the Marks
OL,20,Fand Spencer store.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G1/5
