OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F422A1772193828
OL,3,CWoman hit by car in retail park had
OL,4,Cbeen 'dedicated' teacher
OL,6,FThe driver of a cream and black
OL,7,FRenault Captur car remained at the
OL,8,Fscene to assist officers with their
OL,9,Fenquiries. Northumbria Police say an
OL,10,Finvestigation is ongoing into the
OL,11,Fcollision.
OL,13,FIn a tribute to Ms Grimshaw, her
OL,14,Ffamily said: "Rita, who was born in
OL,15,FTeesside and lived in Whitley Bay,
OL,16,Fdedicated more than 30 years of her
OL,17,Flife to teaching.
OL,26,@vD@NOU
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G2/5
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,423,420,120,260,000,100
PN,42203
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F422A1772193828
OL,3,CWoman hit by car in retail park had
OL,4,Cbeen 'dedicated' teacher
OL,6,F"Throughout her long and distinguished
OL,7,Fcareer, she was known for her
OL,8,Fprofessionalism, compassion, and
OL,9,Funwavering commitment to the children
OL,10,Fand families she supported.
OL,12,F"Outside of her professional life,
OL,13,FRita was a devoted mother to her two
OL,14,Fchildren and a proud grandmother to
OL,15,Ffive.
OL,26,@nD@AOUtD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G3/5
