OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,423,420,120,260,000,100
PN,42204
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F422A1772193828
OL,3,CWoman hit by car in retail park had
OL,4,Cbeen 'dedicated' teacher
OL,6,F"Her family were at the heart of
OL,7,Feverything she did, and she approached
OL,8,Feach role she held with the same
OL,9,Fwarmth, care, and sense of
OL,10,Fresponsibility that defined her
OL,11,Fworking life.
OL,13,F"In her youth, Rita was a keen dancer,
OL,14,Fand those who knew her say that her
OL,15,Fsense of energy and joy stayed with
OL,16,Fher throughout her life."
OL,18,FNorthumbria Police is urging any
OL,19,Fwitnesses or anyone with information
OL,20,Fto contact the force.
OL,26,@nD@AOUuD@AOU
