OL,3,CWoman hit by car in retail park had
OL,4,Cbeen 'dedicated' teacher
OL,6,FSergeant Greg Huntley, of Northumbria
OL,7,FPolice, said: "Our thoughts remain
OL,8,Fwith Rita's family and friends
OL,9,Ffollowing her tragic death and we
OL,10,Fcontinue to support them in any way
OL,11,Fthat we can.
OL,13,F"The investigation into the
OL,14,Fcircumstances surrounding the incident
OL,15,Fis very much ongoing and I would urge
OL,16,Fanyone who has information which could
OL,17,Fassist us but has not yet come forward
OL,18,Fto please to do so."
OL,26,@oD@OOUuD@AOU
